---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Wire Pegs for Windy Conditions"
  description="Thicker wire stainless steel pegs designed for extra grip in windy conditions. Stays on the line when others blow off."
>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-navy-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-4">Specialty · Windy Conditions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy-900 leading-tight mb-6">Wire Pegs for Windy Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Thicker wire. Stronger grip. Stays on the line when the wind picks up.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Built for Australian weather</h2>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">If you live somewhere that gets strong winds — coastal areas, hilltops, open properties — standard pegs can struggle to hold your washing on the line. These windy conditions pegs are made with thicker wire for extra grip and holding power.</p>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">One customer captured footage of their washing staying firmly on the line during wild storms in South East Queensland — tornado-like winds and not a single item lost.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8 border border-navy-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Best for</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-navy-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Windy locations and exposed properties</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Heavy items like jeans, towels and bedding</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Coastal areas with strong sea breezes</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Anyone who has lost washing in the wind</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="bg-teal-500 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors text-lg">Buy Windy Conditions Pegs at Biome →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-navy-100 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex gap-4">
      <a href="/products" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">← All Products</a>
      <a href="/products/jumbo" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">View Jumbo Pegs →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>